OL,3,CMore than 700 drivers handed litter
OL,4,Cfines as part of 'wild wee' row
OL,6,FHundreds of penalties have been issued
OL,7,Fto people who relieved themselves at
OL,8,Fthe side of just one road, it has
OL,9,Femerged.
OL,11,FDacorum Borough Council has become
OL,12,Fembroiled in a "wild wee" row after it
OL,13,Fissued 762 fixed penalty notices to
OL,14,Fmotorists who urinated on a lay-by on
OL,15,Fthe A41 near Kings Langley last year.
OL,17,FThe council revealed more than 985 of
OL,18,Fall the fines issued in 2023 were
OL,19,Fdished out at lay-bys on the A41 near
OL,20,FKing's Langley, according to figures
OL,21,Fseen by the BBC.
