OL,6,FOne those fined was 73-year-old Tony
OL,7,FLeach, who was driving from Maidstone
OL,8,Fin Kent to his granddaughter's 18th
OL,9,Fbirthday when he stopped at an A41
OL,10,Flayby near King's Langley last
OL,11,FNovember.
OL,13,FHe said: "I chose a spot that was
OL,14,Funlikely to cause any offence to
OL,15,Fanybody.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
