OL,3,CMore than 700 drivers handed litter
OL,4,Cfines as part of 'wild wee' row
OL,6,F"But when I turned around there was a
OL,7,Fguy right behind me who said I was on
OL,8,Fcamera and that he was issuing me a
OL,9,Ffixed penalty notice for an apparent
OL,10,Fbreach of the Environmental Protection
OL,11,FAct. I was pretty cheesed off."
OL,13,FMr Leach said: "It beggars belief.
OL,14,FThey are treating motorists as cash
OL,15,Fcows.
OL,17,F"The other thing that bothers me is
OL,18,Fthey are finding motorists relieving
OL,19,Fthemselves for littering, but have
OL,20,Fthey looked at that road?
