OL,6,F"There's loads of real litter there
OL,7,Fwhich is not actually being dealt
OL,8,Fwith."
OL,10,FThe council has also been criticised
OL,11,Fby Nick Freeman, a lawyer popularly
OL,12,Fknown as Mr Loophole, after it fined
OL,13,FMichael Mason, from Winslow,
OL,14,FBuckinghamshire, for littering when he
OL,15,Frelieved himself at the lay-by last
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FSpeaking to BBC Three Countries Radio,
OL,19,FMr Freeman said: "My reaction is that
OL,20,Fthose monies belong to the taxpayer,
OL,21,Fthey should be returned."
