OL,6,FMr Freeman called for Dacorum Borough
OL,7,FCouncil to be "criminally investigated
OL,8,Ffor their continuing practice of
OL,9,Ffining people for taking a 'wild wee'
OL,10,Funder environmental legislation."
OL,12,FThe council has previously said:
OL,13,F"Fixed Penalty Notices (FPNs) are
OL,14,Fissued for urinating in public laybys,
OL,15,Falong a busy stretch of the A41 dual
OL,16,Fcarriageway, and not 'wild wees' in
OL,17,Fwoodlands or countryside."
